      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Editorial and technical review:</strong> We verify European eligibility, documentation
        quality, governance structure, and maintenance status according to our criteria.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Publication and promotion:</strong> If approved, the project is published on the website
        and GitHub repository, gaining visibility within the European community.
      </li>
    </ol>

    <h5>6.4 Project removal and discretionary decisions</h5>
